{"tid":1258764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新華社斥極少數人在中美關稅問題鼓吹投降論","createTime":"2019-06-26T09:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T09:49:46.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"31ae0dc623e936fa477febe50735b731ff33ea34","tid":1258764,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T09:20:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1465144_1_20190626165850.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1465144_1_20190626165850.jpg&h=b55b1d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新華社發表評論文章，表示中國面對美國政府揮舞關稅大棒的「極限施壓」，中國人民應發出萬眾一心的強大力量，但坊間有極少數抱守祟美、媚美、恐美思想的人，時不時出來說風涼話，甚至鼓吹投降論。<br />\n<br />\n評論認為，舉國上下同心應對中美經貿摩擦「兩軍對壘」，需要警惕這些「手榴彈向後扔」的人，必須對這些錯誤思想加以揭露，堅決抵制。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，從歷史教訓，面對霸凌主義，無原則的隱忍退讓都是自我發展機會的喪失，委曲求全換來的都是「得寸進尺」，最終只會任人欺凌。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465144-20190626.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465144-20190626.htm&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=a3d048f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465144-20190626.htm&h=bcf46020\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465144-20190626.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2456f9ef97bb2b4236385820e4cb2891e081aced","tid":1258764,"uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T09:21:12.000Z","msg":"不！<br />\n<br />\n我支持你支那狗去硬撼美帝<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好投降, 打至最後一蚊！"},{"pid":"04c61136a6d2f806a97e30122ab07ee23fcf6b43","tid":1258764,"uid":174295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T09:21:48.000Z","msg":"迫習近平炒車?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06805eaa30f6e5c58202dd130564913748f56081","tid":1258764,"uid":17008,"like":1,"di